807
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:07,480
Hello.

808
00:53:10,750 --> 00:53:12,880
- Why are you here?
- I can ask you the same thing.

809
00:53:15,990 --> 00:53:17,090
Are you looking for Si-ah?

810
00:53:17,990 --> 00:53:18,990
