things from me again for my sake.

858
00:55:55,480 --> 00:55:57,320
Gosh. Okay.

859
00:56:00,990 --> 00:56:01,990
By the way,

860
00:56:02,790 --> 00:56:04,560
how did you all get here?

861
00:56:04,960 --> 00:56:05,960
Well,

862
00:56:06,860 --> 00:56:10,160
